nodes.text: Ganarog was a male Sith Lord of the reconstituted Sith Empire living during the Galactic War. Ganarog was present inside Darth Vengean's Compound when Lord Draahg and another apprentice of Darth Baras stormed the compound in 3642 BBY, intending to kill Darth Vengean on their master's orders. Ganarog engaged the intruders, but was defeated.
